'''Veizen fever''' was a malady that was rumored to cause the [[Moocher]]s of [[Abregado-rae/Legends|Abregado-rae]] to fly into fits of madness. An outbreak of Veizen fever was rumored to have affected one particular colony of Moochers, who were terrorizing other denizens of their [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] by plundering food supplies and attacking anyone who wandered too close to their den.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

